{"about_the_game":"Radikal Fighters is an explosive action-packed game where you and up to four of your friends can dive into two electrifying game modes. Strategize solo or with your teammates to cover the most ground, and thwart your opponents' efforts in this fast-paced, color-splattered frenzy.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073930/extras/SteamSS1.png?t=1728639197\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Modes</strong></h2><strong>Battle Royale </strong><br>Dive into a chaotic free-for-all where only the last fighter standing wins. Explore the vibrant streets of Radikal City, and watch out for hazards and surprises.<br><br><strong>Paint Rush</strong><br>Team up and unleash your creativity in a race against time to paint the town with your team's colors. It's all about covering as much ground as possible before the clock runs out.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Customizables</strong></h2>Equip your unique perks, weapons, and gear to outsmart, outfight (and out-look!) other players in fast-paced, intense battles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Play with friends</strong></h2>Bring your friends into the mix and heat up the city together. Whether you're diving into Battle Royale or teaming up in Paint Rush, bring your crew of up to 4 fighters for maximum wreckage.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073930/extras/Steam_Friends2.gif?t=1728639197\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Mod at first sight","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2073930/b857a70f4f8148cde2b1b8e47901ff3e05ff25d3.jpg"},{"name":"From me to me","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2073930/575e030bcb48bfef4b2ee8d8185fe9a9ddd5f7b4.jpg"},{"name":"My way or the highway","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2073930/2cb17e6655f3085ecf8e81dc9b7e0afd5d958